{
  "texts": [
    "We examined multiple databases, including Google Scholar, GeoRef, and Scopus, to capture a wide range of studies.",
    "Advanced search strings incorporating Boolean logic, such as 'fossil identification AND LSTM' and '3D imaging AND deep learning,' were employed to filter the publications effectively.",
    "The search includes works published from 2017 up to and including June 2024 (investigated on November 15, 2024), ensuring the inclusion of contemporary studies and the latest advancements in the field.",
    "This survey includes studies that are predominantly centered on DL methodologies and their implementation in microfossil image analysis.",
    "Studies that did not have DL as their core focus were excluded."
  ]
}